-- Ambac posts $3.3 billion quarterly loss
-- 
-- Tue Jan 22, 2008 8:07am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/22/businesspro-ambac-results-dc-idUSWNAS705920080122

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bond insurer Ambac Financial Group Inc 
ABK.N on Tuesday reported a quarterly loss of $3.3 billion 
after credit derivative losses totaling $5.2 billion. 

  On a per-share basis, Ambac's fourth-quarter loss was 
$31.85.  In the year ago quarter Ambac earned $202.7 million, or 
$1.88, a share.  (Reporting by  Christian Plumb ; editing by John Wallace)